{"word":"κυβερνήτης","slug":"κυβερνήτης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κυβερνήτης</b></el> <el>(κῠβερνήτης, ου,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κυβερνάω'><el>κυβερνάω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a steersman, helmsman, pilot</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>gubernator</el>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>: ionic <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <el>κυβερνήτεα</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>a guide, governor</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}